係咪又要喺床上面六粒鐘都瞓唔到<br />\n嗰六粒鍾就一直努力合埋眼逼自己瞓<br />\n<br />\n到底我幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知失眠同情緒病有關係 但明明我之前情緒病最嚴重時都無失眠 點解依加會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:01:14.000Z","msg":"做運動實訓倒"},{"pid":"a4701b16328557d1eed06f2894827b5af0968cb1","tid":1901274,"uid":154400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:04:23.000Z","msg":"晚晚瞓左3個鐘就會醒 好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d8fc2ae18be7d52e28677a5b881b15a75c492d","tid":1901274,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54c4494b75e31726959839dead8d09f8a4e94455","tid":1901274,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c3ec123244c4e3b19c31d383903de6c7852ad93","tid":1901274,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"瞓唔到 今晚有啲眼瞓 心諗會瞓到<br />\n最後都係瞓唔到 依加直程無曬睡意<br />\n<br />\n好不安好恐懼 我係咪又要瞓唔到<br />\n係咪又要喺床上面六粒鐘都瞓唔到<br />\n嗰六粒鍾就一直努力合埋眼逼自己瞓<br />\n<br />\n到底我幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知失眠同情緒病有關係 但明明我之前情緒病最嚴重時都無失眠 點解依加會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:01:14.000Z","msg":"做運動實訓倒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"咪話唔係攰唔攰嘅問題係個腦唔肯停嘅問題"},{"pid":"3763650983e40dcf95d7a4d5ad3137513fae8b58","tid":1901274,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:10:28.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣<br />\n<br />\n好驚夜晚訓覺<br />\n<br />\n根本訓唔到"},{"pid":"96837fe9cd0dff6c2915cc572347d09b95a03126","tid":1901274,"uid":151451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:14:29.000Z","msg":"樓豬我同你一樣 或者我敢講我嚴重過你<br />\n<br />\n10點半瞓上床熄燈想瞓 一路碌一路碌 碌碌吓望一望電話 發覺已經凌晨4點 我不斷打自己個頭 將個頭大大地hum落牆度 好撚崩潰 好憎自己點解連瞓教咁基本嘅事都做唔到 點解自己咁撚廢 然後再嘗試去瞓 見到個天開咗光光地了 慢慢開始無乜意識（我諗係極淺度睡眠）<br />\n<br />\n然後大概朝早10點 11點左右就會醒 大概應該瞓咗三四個鐘<br />\n<br />\n已經持續差唔多兩個月了 每日隻眼都好撚攰好撚腫 個眼袋黑眼圈就越嚟越大 脾氣越嚟越暴躁 郁啲就發嬲<br />\n<br />\n食過安眠藥 褪黑激素都無乜野用 已經半放棄狀態了<br />\n<br />\n反正人生都無乜希望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36bd5453b98d11f832b552458209f46a19baf61","tid":1901274,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/MolangOfficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FMolangOfficial&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=565f9530\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/MolangOfficial</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知對大家有冇效，但一路睇個腦就會一片空白<br />\n安靜到個人可能會好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f1b74809795c6b8d6646bcfc938220c2a4cbec","tid":1901274,"uid":185909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:26:53.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n點算"},{"pid":"41c58aacd8a5b46f139d9f1e58d2292fec9c82b3","tid":1901274,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:33:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=13ggcvTHETw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D13ggcvTHETw&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=03c69ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=13ggcvTHETw</a><br />\n跟住佢動作做 <br />\n你應該做到兩set 如果你仲係訓唔到就做4set<br />\n訓唔到你話我聽"},{"pid":"fac05be9fb6f757877e3d9676b048616fb45c75b","tid":1901274,"uid":311275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:35:19.000Z","msg":"我反而係想訓教 身體攰但入唔到睡 個腦好精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過唔緊要啦反正而加都唔洗早起身 日日唔訓都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d610f18b7be69c1db4f95929c1cf351b4882f9","tid":1901274,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"失眠恐懼症 我之前都有"},{"pid":"40ff58203327f033b21e5a4df40a0b77b88c1ad0","tid":1901274,"uid":204363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T19:57:48.000Z","msg":"Download newlife330依個app<br />\n跟住入面d指示做 <br />\n內容大概係類似冥想嘅野 <br />\n之前失眠左3個月 同你一樣 安眠藥都冇用<br />\n用左個app一排之後就好d<br />\n有咩問題可以問我 真心過來人"},{"pid":"044c2ae5e1b71228c3b37ff421e925bb292e5244","tid":1901274,"uid":241444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T20:09:11.000Z","msg":"我都失眠呀 唉 6月依加冇一晚訓得好"},{"pid":"072a7fab189df3621082796e32057004b3aba64e","tid":1901274,"uid":291690,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T20:13:06.000Z","msg":"漸漸失去了訓覺呢個技能<br />\n以前訓足12個鐘夜晚都輕鬆再訓12個鐘<br />\n依家日訓6個鐘,夜晚都係眼光光到4,5點先訓到<br />\n明明2,3點已經有睡意想訓 <br />\n暫時最差情況係失眠間個腦亂諗野<br />\n不停覺得自己好廢 一無是處 只係帶比人負擔<br />\n諗諗諗 諗到喊 喊完一輪先訓到<br />\n呢個月情況特別嚴重<br />\n都唔sure係咪depression 有時情緒都算正常<br />\n放棄了 佛系訓覺 <br />\n身體頂唔順自然訓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82ea79b0bfb0581e9671a63ee1c90c05baa19fa","tid":1901274,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T23:06:46.000Z","msg":"扑完野易訓好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fefcd8b72326577c82809f82a0000731da0292c","tid":1901274,"uid":53261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T23:10:05.000Z","msg":"褪黑色素幫到你"},{"pid":"994b983a5112007b4640d7fc44965d4856e7c666","tid":1901274,"uid":263087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"食埋藥會好好多 按時食藥之後去瞓覺 你睇完醫生佢應該都會俾埋一段時間嘅藥你 應該就冇嘢了"},{"pid":"50db988605626b6a736a54b668e402d5f55fb562","tid":1901274,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994b983a5112007b4640d7fc44965d4856e7c666","tid":1901274,"uid":263087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:29:49.000Z","msg":"食埋藥會好好多 按時食藥之後去瞓覺 你睇完醫生佢應該都會俾埋一段時間嘅藥你 應該就冇嘢了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你"},{"pid":"6f5ad98480427e7117a2dfe7b1d85a7092254bec","tid":1901274,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b5093f3df9f5ea51679cd7f1199c6f6ce20ebb4","tid":1901274,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bdb4191568a395464e79e087a4ac6be390ce57e","tid":1901274,"uid":147800,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"前排成日訓唔著 而家都有時訓唔多著 因為失戀 成日會諗住佢啲野 又想知佢過成點 又想知佢會唔會記起下我 但明明都唔撚再關我事 有時諗到佢同ex幸福過 而自己就同佢拍得一陣拖 比唔到幸福佢 擁有唔到佢 就好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日返工 無咩地方減到壓 平時放工就同朋友打下機開住skype吹下水 表面笑得好開心唔care佢地講我啲咩 話我拍得一陣有咩好唔開心 又話你而家咪笑得傾得幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通我下下要喊住咁講野咩 轉個頭上到床又自己獨單一個 又喊 眼濕濕咁聽住歌 晚晚都4點先訓得著 第2日又要返工 一時8點要起身 一時10點 真係唔可以低估愛情既力量 因為我真係投入左愛先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"我原本4點幾5點先瞓到 開咗學好返啲 好快瞓到（1粒鍾內） 今個星期突然就完全失眠 6點先勉強瞓到一陣 但9點就會自動紮醒 琴晚又係朝早6點打後先瞓到... 個頭痛足兩日 好想死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=f56287cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=b931c27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a> ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"a9726fc8e7a0e9bd78b986c0fd8095b2fb0583de","tid":1901274,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"試試5-htp + 褪黑色素 + L-Theanine <br />\n臨訓前10分鐘食<br />\n我覺得幾有用"},{"pid":"b6d300c48d7d29138afe28a096abb1d24e1a54dc","tid":1901274,"uid":348172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"完全明白樓主感受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前都有一排失眠 每日都驚自己瞓唔著而搞到個人好緊張好驚 甚至最嚴重個陣會食飯個陣望住個鐘係到倒數仲有幾耐要上床瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時瞓到2-3個鐘第朝又要翻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後慢慢安慰自己瞓唔著咪瞓唔著唔洗死 然後先慢慢瞓得著"},{"pid":"a23a97d1a4c22149c13add05c5c79e7492d7fa76","tid":1901274,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d300c48d7d29138afe28a096abb1d24e1a54dc","tid":1901274,"uid":348172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"完全明白樓主感受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前都有一排失眠 每日都驚自己瞓唔著而搞到個人好緊張好驚 甚至最嚴重個陣會食飯個陣望住個鐘係到倒數仲有幾耐要上床瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時瞓到2-3個鐘第朝又要翻學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後慢慢安慰自己瞓唔著咪瞓唔著唔洗死 然後先慢慢瞓得著"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"一諗到瞓唔到我個樣會好殘會生暗瘡我就好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不停同自己講要瞓覺要瞓覺唔係個樣會比現在更加醜"},{"pid":"3acbe4d98323a24b2e82b3c1bcf28dea718f72d4","tid":1901274,"uid":44107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"直上short term安眠藥"}]}